        <li><a href="https://ir.ptcbio.com/news-releases/news-release-details/ptc-therapeutics-announces-fda-approval-sephiencetm-sepiapterin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PTC Therapeutics, Sephience persbericht</a>.</li>
        <li><a href="https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40265-025-02247-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sepiapterin: First Approval</a> (<em>Drugs</em>, 2025).</li>
        <li><a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC6478180/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cochrane Protocol, LNAA bij PKU</a>.</li>
        <li><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17368065/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Schindeler e.a. (2007)</a>: LNAA-suppletie bij klassieke PKU.</li>
        <li><a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC4962165/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ney e.a. (2016)</a>: GMP vs. L-AA, gerandomiseerde trial.</li>
